HEADWORD: Ironwort
<hw>I"ron*wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>An herb of the Mint family (<gen>Sideritis</gen>), supposed to heal
sword cuts; also, a species of <gen>Galeopsis</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

